14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Zararsizlik nuqtasi (ZN) kalkulyatori O'zbekistondagi har qanday tadbirkor uchun muhim vosita hisoblanadi. U daromadlar barcha doimiy va o'zgaruvchan xarajatlarni to'liq qoplovchi minimal sotish hajmini aniqlaydi. Hisoblash formulasi: ZN (dona) = Doimiy xarajatlar / (Birlik narxi − Birlik uchun o'zgaruvchan xarajatlar). Zararsizlik nuqtasini bilish mablag' kiritishdan oldin biznes-rejaning realligini baholash imkonini beradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Doimiy xarajatlar — ishlab chiqarish hajmiga bog'liq bo'lmagan xarajatlar: binoni ijaraga olish, xodimlar ish haqi, kommunal to'lovlar, mol-mulk soliqlari, sug'urta. O'zbekistonda Toshkentda savdo binosi ijarasi joylashuviga qarab oyiga 3 dan 15 mln so'mgacha, 2026-yilda eng kam ish haqi esa 1 271 000 so'mni tashkil etadi. Bu xarajatlar sotish hajmidan qat'i nazar qoplanishi shart."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zgaruvchan xarajatlar sotish hajmiga mutanosib ravishda o'sadi: tovar tannarxi, qadoqlash, yetkazib berish, marketpleyslar komissiyasi (Uzum Market, Sello 5–15% oladi). Sotish narxi va birlik uchun o'zgaruvchan xarajatlar o'rtasidagi farq marjinal foyda deyiladi — aynan shu doimiy xarajatlarni qoplaydi. Marja qanchalik yuqori bo'lsa, biznes shunchalik tez o'zini oqlaydi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Misolni ko'rib chiqaylik: Toshkentda novvoyxona ochmoqchisiz. Doimiy xarajatlar: ijara 5 mln, ish haqi 8 mln, kommunal 2 mln — jami oyiga 15 mln so'm. Non tannarxi 4 000 so'm, sotish narxi 8 000 so'm. ZN = 15 000 000 / (8 000 − 4 000) = oyiga 3 750 dona, ya'ni kuniga taxminan 125 dona non. Bundan ortiq sotilgan har bir non — sof foydangiz."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kalkulyator shuningdek pul ifodasida (so'mda) ZNni, xavfsizlik zaxirasini va o'zini oqlash muddatini hisoblaydi. Bu kredit uchun ariza berishda ayniqsa muhim: O'zbekiston banklari ("}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ipoteka","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"Ipoteka"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":"-bank, Asaka-bank) o'zini oqlash asoslanmasi bilan biznes-rejani talab qiladi. ZNni muntazam qayta hisoblash dollar kursi yoki xom ashyo narxi o'zgarganda narx siyosatini moslashtirishga yordam beradi."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],["$L19"]]}],"$L1a","$L1b"]}]
